snippet.textDisplay: It's the best song produced by  Coke Studio Pakistan this season up until now. I am glad that they are experimenting because as much as I love strings and some of the amazing numbers they have given us in CS, I was waiting for something innovative and different to their style and Ali Hamza and Zohaib Kazi have packed apunch with this mind blowing piece of music. The singers were absolutely incredible. Natasha has such a beautiful and powerful voice she deserves so much respect and admiration for the way she sung this song and so do the Qawwals. Hats off to all of you.
